title: Cassius Turvey: Teen set to work at Gina Rinehart's Roy Hill mine when allegedly 'racially' murdered
description: Tragic teen Cassius Turvey was due to start work at Gina Rinehart's Roy Hill mine in the Pilbara when he was allegedly murdered in what has described as a 'racially motivated' attack.

title: CVS pharmacist charged in 2017 Delphi murders posed up for a photo near 'wanted' sketch
description: Bob Matlock, owner of JC's Bar in Delphi, Indiana, said on Monday the man arrested for the 2017 murder of two teenage girls in the town was a regular among his patrons.

title: Britons have never been happier than the moment Covid lockdown was lifted, research suggests
description: In the 12 months to March - as all legal restrictions were dropped in February - average life satisfaction was 7.54 out of ten, up from 7.39 the previous year, according to the ONS.

title: Tory Right backs Suella Braverman over private email storm
description: The embattled Home Secretary faced Labour calls to resign over the lapses in email security which led to her being sacked by then PM Liz Truss last month.

title: Pelosi says husband Paul is 'making steady progress' after home intruder attacked him with a hammer
description: Paul Pelosi, who was the only one home when DePape broke in, called the police who arrived two minutes later to find the 82-year-old and DePape, 42, struggling over a hammer.

title: Permacrisis and partygate... what a year! Dictionary compilers reveal the words that define 2022
description: Other words that make this year's cut include 'partygate', for the scandal over lockdown gatherings at Downing Street and 'sportswashing'.

title: Heartbreaking video shows three-year-old dog 'Bob' that NO ONE wants during adoption event in NYC
description: One New York City pup has become the the talk of the 'Tok,' TikTok that is, after he went viral because no one wanted to play with him at a recent NYC adoption event.

title: Halloween trick-or-treating teens caught on camera allegedly stealing lollies from home in Victoria
description: Two teens have been caught on camera opening  the front door of a woman's home and allegedly stealing a bag full of lollies while out trick-or-treating on Halloween.

title: Sydney weather: Boy hit by tree branch during Halloween celebrations, West Pennant Hills
description: A child was struck by a tree branch after 'ridiculous' wild winds battered West Pennant Hills in Sydney's north-west on Monday night.

title: Zakir Slaimankhel v. Qantas: Rugby star breaks silence over flight attendant row
description: Rugby star and charity ambassador Zakir Slaimankhel has broken his silence with a lengthy  Facebook post after he and his family were kicked off a Qantas flight from Bali to Sydney last month.

title: Brighton, Melbourne rocked by knifeman who allegedly broke into homes before police taser
description: Residents in Brighton in Melbourne's east got a Halloween fright on Monday after a man allegedly broke into a woman's home sparking a huge police operation.

title: Keir Starmer vows to force tech giants to pay for news if Labour triumphs at the ballot box
description: Sir Keir Starmer has signalled that Labour would force tech giants to pay news publishers for their content if the party wins the next election.

title: The Crown star Elizabeth Debicki urges critics to stop complaining about show's plotlines
description: Elizabeth Debicki, who plays Princess Diana in the upcoming season of the Netflix show, said it was an 'interpretation' of events and 'we can maybe stop talking' about the controversy.
